title: Panic at the Discord
description: Katie and Ashley have some big news about the pod, and Austin has some big news about dinosaurs. Then, a mental health update before an all-question podcast, including: is a refrigerator a closet, superpowers, Mario Kart, wine glasses, Survivor, potatoes, sneezing, and more. Finally, Myrtle makes a cameo.

itunes:subtitle: Katie and Ashley answer ALL of your most pressing questions?
